title: Welcome to our affiliate program
layout_update_xml:
<referenceContainer name="root" htmlTag="div" htmlClass="affiliate-programs-daytours">
</referenceContainer>
<referenceContainer name="header.container.banner">
            <block class="Magento\Cms\Block\Block" name="banne_affiliate_banner" before="-">
                <arguments>
                    <argument name="block_id" xsi:type="string">become-seller-banner</argument>
                </arguments>
            </block>
        </referenceContainer>

        <referenceContainer name="content">
            <container name="main.container.affiliate" as="main_container_affiliate" label="" htmlTag="div" htmlClass="container main-content-becom-seller" >
                <block class="Magento\Cms\Block\Block" name="affiliate_content_main" before="-">
                    <arguments>
                        <argument name="block_id" xsi:type="string">affiliate-content-main</argument>
                    </arguments>
                </block>
            </container>
        </referenceContainer>

        <referenceContainer name="page.wrapper">
            <container name="container.affiliate.block.black" as="container_affiliate_block_black" label="" htmlTag="div" htmlClass="container-affiliate-block-black" after="main.content" >
                <container name="container.affiliate.block.black.content" as="container_affiliate_block_black_content" label="" htmlTag="div" htmlClass="container-affiliate-block-black-content" >
                    <block class="Magento\Cms\Block\Block" name="affiliate_content_black" before="-">
                        <arguments>
                            <argument name="block_id" xsi:type="string">affiliate-black-content</argument>
                        </arguments>
                    </block>
                </container>
            </container>
            <container name="container.affiliate.block.form" as="container_affiliate_block_form" label="" htmlTag="div" htmlClass="container-affiliate-block-form" after="container.affiliate.block.black" >
                <container name="container.affiliate.block.form.content" as="container_affiliate_block_form_content" label="" htmlTag="div" htmlClass="container-affiliate-block-form-content" >
                    <block class="Magento\Customer\Block\Form\Register" name="daytours.affiliate.register.configure" template="Daytours_Affiliate::account/register-configure.phtml" cacheable="false" />
                </container>
            </container>
        </referenceContainer>
<move element="messages" destination="container.affiliate.block.form.content" after="daytours.affiliate.register.configure"/>
